t-size: xx-large;\">而家先識驚？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當日我屌柒班大愛支鳩鐵所謂廿四小時生活圈根本就係大伏，我仲講定等睇鬼佬教壞香港嘅&quot;先醫人後俾錢&quot;到時先和味！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span></strong></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0a4339952a8ebdad3ce9c8ceabf211b44b1369ef","tid":1840353,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你香港都會奶野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而家先識驚？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當日我屌柒班大愛支鳩鐵所謂廿四小時生活圈根本就係大伏，我仲講定等睇鬼佬教壞香港嘅&quot;先醫人後俾錢&quot;到時先和味！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span></strong></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ccd10e3b6a596be6bb520460dcffd17da40938d1","tid":1840353,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:33:19.000Z","msg":"中共死全國，自作孽不可活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9962134127a1ffd9eab6af1fbe1b84b6f7fb9a12","tid":1840353,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d1e69775b4fe708285cf1d03df611510031e98","tid":1840353,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:35:38.000Z","msg":"太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f9beeea37c8fff4662ac68fbb2faf5ccb416c8","tid":1840353,"uid":277363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"14億人一個零頭都冇，怕乜"},{"pid":"d7d101e37792a23656cfed315778bace0a4a4a89","tid":1840353,"uid":329324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ccb469b065d17a05723e01be7740717024c38c5","tid":1840353,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:48:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢新型冠狀病毒在中國大爆發，武漢市成為重災區。有外國研究論文估計，武漢市現只發現 5.1% 個案，估計若防疫措施不變，預測 10 日後（2月4日）感染人數會高達 27 萬人。學者指，新型冠狀病毒的傳播系數為 1 比 3.6 至 4，即比沙士 1 比 3 的情況更嚴重，強調須控制 72% 至 75% 感染個案，才可阻止感染數字繼續增加。<br />\n<br />\n研究論文昨日發表，撰寫的學者來自英國蘭開斯特大學、格拉斯哥 Medical Research Council-University of Glasgow Centre for Virus Research，以及美國佛羅里達大學等。<br />\n<br />\n論文指出，新型冠狀病毒的傳播系數為 1 比 3.6 至 4，即 1 人可傳染多達 4 人，須有效控制 72% 至 75% 傳染個案，才可阻止感染數字繼續增加。<br />\n<br />\n學者估計，武漢市現時只發現 5.1% 的個案，顯示社區中仍有大量感染個案，而且檢測病毒困難，強調一旦防疫措施不變，病毒將會在其他中國城市爆發，輸出其他國家的個案將會不斷增加。<br />\n<br />\n透過模型預測，10 日後，亦即 2 月 4 日，武漢市受感染人數將會在 13 萬人至 27 萬人之間，上海、北京、廣州、重慶及成都會是其他最大爆發的城市。他們預計，上海感染人數超過 900 人，北京感染人數達 786 人，相信全國春運是助長疫情的原因之一。模型亦預測，香港、日本、台灣、韓國最容易透過航空途經輸入受感染的病人。<br />\n</span></span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"10日後應該沖破一萬人"}]}